title: San Diego/Downtown
name: William Heath Davis House
price: Walking tours $15 adults, $12 seniors/students/military, children under 12 free; Davis House $5 adults, $4 seniors
content: The headquarters of the Gaslamp Quarter Historical Foundation, the visitor center here offers information for self-guided tours of the district as well as a guided walking tour of the district that leaves every Saturday at 11AM.
